the only secure way to offer a file from app to another app
    -   content URI                     -   send the receiving app the file's content URI and
    -   temporary access permissions    -   grant temporary access permissions to that URI

Content URIs with temporary URI access permissions
    -   apply only to receiving app
    -   expire automatically

The Android FileProvider component
    -   getUriForFile() -   for generating a file's content URI
